18 kcal"},"usefulItems":"serving bowl, spiralizer or julienne peeler , refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["The ingredients can be doubled to serve 12 as part of a buffet.","If you don't have a spiralizer, use a julienne peeler or peel courgette into ribbons with a standard peeler and slice thinly lengthways."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","40m","6 portions"]}